- Constants: 6 (`"component"`, `0.5` via binding, `0.3` via binding, `0` reduce init, `0.2`, `2`) × 1 = 3 raw (`"component"`, `0` init, `0.2`, `2`) = 4
- Bindings: 17 (`customer`, `typedCustomer`, `items`, `typed`, `COMPONENT_BLOCK_SIZE`, `i`, `isComponentBlock`, `COMPONENT_BLOCK_PREMIUM`, `basePremium`, `PROCESSING_FEE`, `sum`, `item`, `itemBase`, `CURSED_SURCHARGE_RATE`, `cursedSurcharge`, `HIGH_ENCHANTMENT_THRESHOLD`, `HIGH_ENCHANTMENT_SURCHARGE_RATE`, `enchantmentSurcharge`, `loyaltyDiscount`, `BASE_PREMIUMS`) × 1 = 20
